{"id":6629,"date":"2024-01-12T16:55:17","date_gmt":"2020-03-12T11:25:17","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=6629"},"modified":"2024-07-11T12:48:54","modified_gmt":"2024-07-11T07:18:54","slug":"window-decoration-ideas","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-decor\/window-decoration-ideas\/","title":{"rendered":"Window Decoration Ideas For Your Home"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Say bye to a dull window with these decoration ideas for your home<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>You&#8217;ve heard of home decor, but what about window decor? Often ignored is a window, and not having a clue on how to decorate your window can be a head-scratching situation. Give your windows a whole new look. Check out these five window decoration ideas for your home.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Kitchen Window Decoration Ideas<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>As an old saying goes, a kitchen is the heart of the home, a place where we eat, drink and be merry and sometimes also look out of the window.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let us ask you a quick question. How well have you utilized your window space? Most of you will answer \u201cUh well we haven\u2019t.\u201d Well now is the time to brighten up your dull windows. No one can get enough oxygen in fact we need more of it. Decorating your window with plants will bring in a sweet earthy feel for your kitchen.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignnone wp-image-6635 size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21012259\/kitchen-window-decorating-ideas.jpg\" alt=\"Kitchen window decorating ideas where can decorate with plants will bring in a sweet earthy feel.\" class=\"wp-image-6635\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21012259\/kitchen-window-decorating-ideas.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21012259\/kitchen-window-decorating-ideas-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21012259\/kitchen-window-decorating-ideas-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21012259\/kitchen-window-decorating-ideas-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Small plants placed in white ceramic pots for a fresh look in your kitchen<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, check out\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/5-best-diy-decor-hacks-for-your-home\/\">5 Best DIY Decor Hacks For Your Home<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Halloween Window Decoration Ideas<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>\u201cIt\u2019s Halloween; everyone\u2019s entitled to one good scare.\u201d Isn\u2019t it always a pleasure to scare your family and friends and then have a good long laugh about it? \u2018Uhh, yeah. Every home has windows large, small, tiny and tall. Every window deserves to put on its best show this Halloween. Pumpkins never go out style, get your tools out and start carving. You can place scary-face carved pumpkins on your window ledge. Amp up the spooky quotient with candles right in the middle.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Why not hang some spiders on their webs? Wool and pipe cleaners will do the job. Create your spiders using black pipe-cleaners and their webs using a yarn of white wool and cotton. This is sure to keep your guests at their toes.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Rusty orange and brown leaves to give the seasons a feel are a must. Orange and brown leaves add to the rustic look and blend in well with pumpkins. Be sure to stick a few on your windows for a touch and feel the experience. Keep your spooky spirits high by lighting colored candles and placing them by the windowsills.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignnone wp-image-6634 size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21012256\/halloween-window-decoration-ideas-for-home.jpg\" alt=\"Halloween window decoration ideas add orange and brown leaves look rustic and blend in well with pumpkins.\" class=\"wp-image-6634\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21012256\/halloween-window-decoration-ideas-for-home.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21012256\/halloween-window-decoration-ideas-for-home-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21012256\/halloween-window-decoration-ideas-for-home-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21012256\/halloween-window-decoration-ideas-for-home-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Orange and brown leaves for a rustic feel with pumpkins and spider to complete a perfect look this Halloween<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, check out <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/fun-and-easy-summer-decor-ideas\/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">10 Easy Summer Decorating Ideas For Your Home<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Home interiors that promise an instant upgrade!\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/11122626\/home-interiors-that-promise-instant-upgrade.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Cheap Window Decoration Ideas<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Leave a little sparkle wherever you go? Why not by your window? Fairy lights have been used in many different ways over the years, to decorate bed-sides to bottles, string picture displays to mirrors. If you want to add beautiful appeal to your window, why not take the help of fairy lights? Drape fairy lights across your window frames and let them drop by the ledge to spark up your home.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignnone wp-image-6632 size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21012249\/cheap-home-window-decoration-ideas.jpg\" alt=\"Home window decoration ideas try fairy lights across your window frames and let them drop by the ledge to spark up.\" class=\"wp-image-6632\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21012249\/cheap-home-window-decoration-ideas.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21012249\/cheap-home-window-decoration-ideas-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21012249\/cheap-home-window-decoration-ideas-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21012249\/cheap-home-window-decoration-ideas-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Fairy lights wrapped across the windowsill to give a luminous warm effect<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, check out <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/home-decorating-ideas-on-a-budget\/\">Home Decorating Ideas On A Budget<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Large Window Sill Decorating Ideas<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you have a large window and you have no clue what to do with it, well why don\u2019t you get, set grow? A large window has an added advantage in terms of ventilation and light. But a window sill with nothing on it can be a turnoff. Plants like mini cactus, succulents, and germanium make a perfect window sill garden and can easily be maintained. You can put them in colorful pots and vases to make sure they stand out.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignnone wp-image-6636 size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21012303\/large-window-sill-decorating-ideas.jpg\" alt=\"Large window sill decorating ideas go for miniature gardens to make a perfect window.\" class=\"wp-image-6636\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21012303\/large-window-sill-decorating-ideas.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21012303\/large-window-sill-decorating-ideas-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21012303\/large-window-sill-decorating-ideas-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21012303\/large-window-sill-decorating-ideas-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A miniature garden created on a windowsill with a set of personalised plants<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Glass Window Decoration Ideas<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Big glass windows looking pale and lonely? Not anymore! Create a little drama with drapes. Luxurious velvet drapes in colours of red gold and violet or rusty browns will give a classy finish to your glassy windows. You can also have curtains with lavish laces or subtle sequence work if you want that extra glam.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignnone wp-image-6633 size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21012252\/glass-window-curtain-decoration-ideas.jpg\" alt=\"Glass window decoration is one of the best window curtain decoration ideas for your home.\" class=\"wp-image-6633\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21012252\/glass-window-curtain-decoration-ideas.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21012252\/glass-window-curtain-decoration-ideas-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21012252\/glass-window-curtain-decoration-ideas-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/21012252\/glass-window-curtain-decoration-ideas-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Rich blue curtains hanging down from a huge glass window bring out a lavish look<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Did you like what you just read? Well, this was what we thought were ways to decorate your windows at home. We would love to hear how you have decorated your windows. Leave your suggestions in the comments section below.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, check out\u00a0 <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-decor\/home-decor-trends\/\">Latest Home Design And Decor Trends 2024<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Looking For Functional Interior Designs?<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with smart solutions<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-label\" id=\"labeltxt\">Enter your name*<\/span>  -->\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"form-row dc-falg-row\">\n        <!-- <div class=\"form-group col-md-3 guideForm\">\n            <select name=\"your-phone-ext\" id=\"id_select2_example\" class=\"id_select2_example drop-downfield form-dropdown\"\n                onfocus='this.size=5;' onblur='this.size=1;' onchange='this.size=1; this.blur();'\n                data-width=\"100%\" data-minimum-results-for-search=\"Infinity\">\n               \n                <option value=\"+01\"\n                    data-img_